<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/mar/22/">&#x27a0;</a> March 22, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="media-molecule-we-make-games" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.mediamolecule.com/games.html">Media Molecule - We make games.</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>This month&#8217;s issue of Edge practically creams itself over the game which is now named &#8220;Little Big Planet&#8221;.  Watching this preview video, it certainly looks like it could be fun, but it&#8217;s not convincing me I need to rush out and drop $600 on a PS3 like Edge suggested it would.</p>

